metadata.name: WMVG #0 Party Bid Token
metadata.description:
Unfortunately, we were not able to get Party Bid to work with an auction, but we did not want to miss out on a potentially legendary/historical piece of artwork. Hence, we are creating this token that will be then party bid on. 

All of the proceeds from the party bid will then be put to use to bid on the WMVG #0.
